*  String Appending Operation

  Step 1: [ Initialization ]
          i = 0
          l = 0

  Step 2: [ To reach at end of text ] 
          For(i=0;str1[i] != '\0';i++)
              l = l + 1

  Step 3: [ Append a string ]
            Fro(i=0;str2[i] != '\0';i++)
                str1[l + i - 1] = str2[i]

  Step 4:  [ Print the string after appending]
            print(""str1)

  Step 5: [ Finished ] & Exit
